</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A driver trying to avoid a head-on crash with a motorcycle approaching in the 
wrong lane swerved his station wagon into the opposite lane Sunday and killed 
three other motorcycle riders, the California Highway Patrol said. 
</P>
<P>
 The crash near this town 27 miles north of San Francisco closed Highway 1 for 
3 1/2 hours. 
</P>
